Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.52,0:21:18.46,ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H0080ffff}{\frz-90}你恬然沉睡 梦境已被解开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.53,0:21:24.07,ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H0080ff80}誰もいない
